{"id": "422167", "revid": "49740203", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=422167", "title": "Empire's Fall (quest)", "text": "Objectives.\nCollect a Felbreaker's Tome and the Sigil of the Sorcerer King from &lt;a href=\"Highmaul\"&gt;Highmaul&lt;/a&gt;.\nDescription.\nThe Ogre Sorcerer King, &lt;a href=\"Imperator%20Mar%27gok%20%28alternate%20universe%29\"&gt;Imperator Mar'gok&lt;/a&gt;, has mastered magical techniques we would consider on the fringe of arcane science. His felbreakers, among others, can actively dampen or nullify magic. Even fel magic!\nIf we're to locate , we need to figure out how it's done. Acquire a felbreaker's tome from his felbreaker captain and acquire the sigil of the sorcerer king himself - I must know what he knows.\nYes, &lt;name&gt;, this means I expect you to storm Highmaul and defeat everyone inside. Get to it!\nRewards.\nYou will receive: \nProgress.\nWhat have you found in Highmaul?\nCompletion.\nThe felbreaker's tome is blank? Let me see that. Did you get the Sorcerer King's sigil? Of course - see here, as you run the sigil over the page, runic lettering appears. Oh... this is really advanced.\nIt may take some time to fully comprehend what you've discovered, &lt;name&gt;, but these initial pages appear to be dedicated to the nature of fel. Exactly what I need! Great work!\n\"On complete\"\nNotes.\nPick up &lt;a href=\"Legacy%20of%20the%20Sorcerer%20Kings\"&gt;Legacy of the Sorcerer Kings&lt;/a&gt; before heading out.\nThe &lt;a href=\"Felbreaker%27s%20Tome\"&gt;Felbreaker's Tome&lt;/a&gt; drops from &lt;a href=\"Ko%27ragh\"&gt;Ko'ragh&lt;/a&gt;, and the &lt;a href=\"Sigil%20of%20the%20Sorcerer%20King\"&gt;Sigil of the Sorcerer King&lt;/a&gt; drops from &lt;a href=\"Imperator%20Mar%27gok%20%28tactics%29\"&gt;Imperator Mar'gok&lt;/a&gt; in all difficulty modes, including &lt;a href=\"Raid%20Finder\"&gt;Raid Finder&lt;/a&gt;."}
