put the plagued wretches out of their misery before Mal'Ganis can claim their souls.\"\nCaverns of Time.\nPlayers are able to experience this event in the &lt;a href=\"Culling%20of%20Stratholme%20%28instance%29\"&gt;Caverns of Time: Culling of Stratholme&lt;/a&gt; in \"\"."}
