the world of the living and run back up the stairs to the Temple of Kimbul, which is now filled with &lt;a href=\"Ancient%20Spirit%20%28Vol%27dun%29\"&gt;Ancient Spirits&lt;/a&gt;. Talk to Kimbul to turn in.\nOn completion:"}
