{"id": "658682", "revid": "38791128", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=658682", "title": "The Curse of Stone", "text": "The Curse of Stone is a book looted from the &lt;a href=\"Corrupted%20Chest\"&gt;Corrupted Chest&lt;/a&gt; after defeating &lt;a href=\"Alleria%20Windrunner%20%28Vision%20of%20Stormwind%29\"&gt;Alleria Windrunner&lt;/a&gt; in the &lt;a href=\"Vision%20of%20Stormwind\"&gt;Vision of Stormwind&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=\"Thrall%20%28Vision%20of%20Orgrimmar%29\"&gt;Thrall&lt;/a&gt; in the &lt;a href=\"Vision%20of%20Orgrimmar\"&gt;Vision of Orgrimmar&lt;/a&gt;. Written by a cultist, it was meant to serve as anti-&lt;a href=\"Titan\"&gt;Titan&lt;/a&gt; propaganda; it aims to document the \"lies of the Titans\" and the \"injustice\" they inflicted upon the denizens of &lt;a href=\"Azeroth\"&gt;Azeroth&lt;/a&gt;. Its name is a twist on the term \"the &lt;a href=\"Curse%20of%20Flesh\"&gt;Curse of Flesh&lt;/a&gt;.\""}
