gy%20Duskbat\"&gt;Mangy Duskbat&lt;/a&gt;s are level 2 and level 3 mobs and can be found east of &lt;a href=\"Deathknell\"&gt;Deathknell&lt;/a&gt; between the village and the &lt;a href=\"Scarlet%20Crusade\"&gt;Scarlet Crusade&lt;/a&gt; camp.\nYou have to complete this quest before you can accept the following quests:"}
