nguarded, in the room just ahead. Upon attempting to loot it, Ariden appears and knocks the player back.\nStage 5: The Rider's Prize.\nHead to the northernmost part of the catacombs and defeat any Dark Riders and Cursed Guardians you encounter along the way.\nStage 6: Reaping the Riders.\nUpon approaching Ariden in the final chamber:\nDuring the fight, Ariden occasionally transforms into a &lt;a href=\"worgen\"&gt;worgen&lt;/a&gt;.\nUpon killing Ariden:\nFinal Stage: The Scythe Reclaimed.\nThe Scythe is stuck on the floor next to Ariden's corpse. Upon looting it, Revil runs into the chamber."}
