ad south to the &lt;a href=\"Tainted%20Scar\"&gt;Tainted Scar&lt;/a&gt; in the &lt;a href=\"Blasted%20Lands\"&gt;Blasted Lands&lt;/a&gt; for &lt;a href=\"Daio%20the%20Decrepit%20%28quest%29\"&gt;Daio the Decrepit (quest)&lt;/a&gt;. Otherwise, use to return to Meryl."}
