layer to bind their &lt;a href=\"Hearthstone\"&gt;Hearthstone&lt;/a&gt; to the inn. Similarly, &lt;a href=\"Grenja\"&gt;Grenja&lt;/a&gt; becomes a repair vendor and &lt;a href=\"Man%27zul\"&gt;Man'zul&lt;/a&gt; becomes a &lt;a href=\"stable%20master\"&gt;stable master&lt;/a&gt;.\nThis concludes the Goldtusk Inn questline. Rhan'ka offers &lt;a href=\"Ruins-Level%20Marketing\"&gt;Ruins-Level Marketing&lt;/a&gt;, a breadcrumb quest to the &lt;a href=\"Court%20of%20Zak%27rajan\"&gt;Court of Zak'rajan&lt;/a&gt;."}
