, they land on a Winged Soul Eater that happens to be passing below them, knocking its unfortunate rider off and taking over the soul eater as their new mount.\nStruggle for Control.\nThe player has three abilities:\nUse each ability when prompted by the Soul Eater's behavior. Each correct usage gives 20% progress on the bar.\nAt 100%, it's time for another cutscene:\nOn the other side of the cutscene, the player finds themselves on the &lt;a href=\"Path%20of%20Inception\"&gt;Path of Inception&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Zereth%20Mortis\"&gt;Zereth Mortis&lt;/a&gt;. The Winged Soul Eater is lying dead on the path in front of them, and Pelagos stands waiting even further ahead into the mist. On approach:\nPTR version.\nIn early builds, the dialogue at the start was slightly different:\nAdditionally, there was some more dialogue in the scene when the Anima Wyrm is chained by the Mawsworn:"}
