pon landing on the platform where Typhinius is:\nUpon engaging Typhinius:\nOn low health:\nOn defeat:\nFinal Stage: Fists of the Heavens.\nInteract with &lt;a href=\"Li%20Li%27s%20Kite\"&gt;Li Li's Kite&lt;/a&gt; to return to the Wandering Isle.\nAfter completing the quest, head outside and back into the Temple of the Five Dawns for the followup quest."}
