e following abilities:\nFinish off the Pyrelord and it will pull all nearby units to it as it dies. As it dies, the ground around it ruptures and players fall down in to the &lt;a href=\"Molten%20Flow\"&gt;Molten Flow&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;a href=\"Thisalee%20Crow\"&gt;Thisalee Crow&lt;/a&gt; is inside to the northeast. Speak with her to continue.\nShe also knows the way out:\nThe Thermal Vent at back at the entrance will launch players to the surface, no head-watching required. To get back to the bottom without liquifying, a Rappelling Rope can be found at the hole's northern edge."}
