nto him.\nMordriss is the highest in level out of the three (at 114), but his health is also \"significantly\" lower. The other two should prove to be no challenge.\nStage 4: Archmage Vargoth.\nAll you need to do here is chat with him.\nStage 5: Grounded.\nFrom this point on, he will follow and assist you.\nStage 6: Stealth Philosophy.\nWait for an opening to appear between the patrolling groups of demons before using &lt;a href=\"Invisibility\"&gt;Invisibility&lt;/a&gt;.\nMake a dash towards the building entrance. Once inside, follow the path ahead to continue to the next stage.\nFinal Stage: The Soulstone's Power.\nThe very first action to do here is &lt;a href=\"Spellsteal\"&gt;Spellsteal&lt;/a&gt; Kathra'natir's Vampiric Aura, which will greatly increase your damage, haste, and grant 100% &lt;a href=\"leech\"&gt;leech&lt;/a&gt;. As a result, the demon should only last long enough to cast Carrion Swarm once (which you should &lt;a href=\"Counterspell\"&gt;Counterspell&lt;/a&gt;).\nUse to leave the scenario."}
