outh fork to find the corpses of the courier and a Krasari Mauler. Interact with the courier:\nImmediately to the south is the &lt;a href=\"Incursion\"&gt;Incursion&lt;/a&gt;, locked in an arcane bubble. is immediately outside. Do the Incursion quests starting with &lt;a href=\"The%20Arcanic%20Oubliette\"&gt;The Arcanic Oubliette&lt;/a&gt; or not, then keep heading along the path south to reach the temple. Koro can be found on the path right as it crosses the river north of the &lt;a href=\"Temple%20of%20the%20Red%20Crane\"&gt;Temple of the Red Crane&lt;/a&gt;."}
